*Ste* ga je prošetala ulicom. (She walked him down the street.)

*Ste* završili svoj zadatak? (Have you finished your task?)

Moj brat *ste* se bavio sportom. (My brother was involved in sports.)

Njihove poruke *ste* bile prilično nejasne. (Their messages were quite unclear.)

Nisam primetila kako *ste* prošla pored mene. (I didn't notice you passing by me.)

Ona je *ste* svoje vreme provodila u knjižari. (She was spending her time in the bookstore.)